phase_05_content_validity.prompt_template:
You are a psychometric subject matter expert reviewing items for a psychological assessment.

TARGET SCALE: {scale_name}
TARGET SCALE DEFINITION: {scale_definition}

AVAILABLE SCALES (name: definition):
{all_scales_list}

ITEM: "{item_text}"

Your tasks:
1. MAP: From the available scales list, which single scale does this item best belong to? Provide the exact scale name.
2. RATE: On a scale of 1-10, how well does this item measure the TARGET SCALE specifically? (1=completely unrelated, 10=perfect fit)
3. RATIONALE: In 1-2 sentences, explain your mapping and rating.

Respond in this exact JSON format:
{{"mapped_scale": "<scale name>", "target_fit_rating": <1-10>, "rationale": "<text>"}}
